553
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:42,280
This is driving me crazy too!

554
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:45,960
Well, you know,

555
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,840
this is what happened.

556
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,720
Professor Hwang got into an accident

557
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:55,080
