804
00:58:52,760 --> 00:58:54,560
Leslie Cheung!

805
00:58:55,360 --> 00:58:58,840
Leslie Cheung!

806
00:59:03,600 --> 00:59:04,600
(Ma Dong-chan)

807
00:59:08,840 --> 00:59:09,960
Finally.

808
00:59:11,400 --> 00:59:12,400
Okay, okay.

809
00:59:18,760 --> 00:59:21,880
Now that I take a proper look,
you've aged so much.

810
00:59:22,120 --> 00:59:23,360
Did you live recklessly?

811
00:59:24,520 --> 00:59:27,000
I forgot to take my botox,
so my skin looks a little saggy.

812
00:59:28,120 --> 00:59:31,600
Plus, I'm the chief,
and I'm pretty old now.

813
00:59:31,680 --> 00:59:33,640
Yes, I know. So what?

814
00:59:37,040 --> 00:59:38,560
-Hello, sir.
-Hello, sir.

815
00:59:38,640 --> 00:59:40,640
Hey, guys. Keep up the good work.

816
00:59:41,680 --> 00:59:44,520
Always focus on sincerity
rather than the ratings.

817
00:59:44,840 --> 00:59:47,440
A director isn't a salesman.
You know that, right?

818
00:59:47,520 --> 00:59:49,000
-Yes, sir!
-Good.

819
00:59:53,120 --> 00:59:54,280
What a joke.

820
00:59:54,720 --> 00:59:57,240
You'd better teach them
how to get good ratings.

821
00:59:57,320 --> 00:59:58,320
Okay.

822
00:59:59,240 --> 01:00:01,880
And is this the army or something?
Why are you being so strict?

823
01:00:20,880 --> 01:00:23,200
(The main anchor for the
nine o'clock news will get replaced.)

824
01:00:24,440 --> 01:00:25,680
(Let's just cover this up.)

825
01:00:25,880 --> 01:00:28,680
We can't do that. We should check
if he's dead or alive.

826
01:00:28,880 --> 01:00:30,360
What if something went wrong and he died?

827
01:00:30,440 --> 01:00:32,120
He's probably dead already!

828
01:00:42,600 --> 01:00:46,240
(I didn't have a choice.
There was nothing I could do.)

829
01:01:13,600 --> 01:01:14,600
Dong-chan.

830
01:01:35,320 --> 01:01:38,240
(Let's kiss each other
until we break our front teeth.)

831
01:01:52,080 --> 01:01:55,480
I'm free on Friday.

832
01:01:56,320 --> 01:01:57,480
Would you like

833
01:01:58,240 --> 01:01:59,320
to meet?

834
01:02:42,720 --> 01:02:45,040
(Melting Me Softly)

835
01:02:45,160 --> 01:02:47,040
(You're a new face.
Have you worked in this field?)

836
01:02:47,120 --> 01:02:48,320
(What do you think you're doing?)

837
01:02:48,400 --> 01:02:49,720
Let's have celebrities go to an island

838
01:02:49,800 --> 01:02:50,840
and make them cook
three meals a day there.

839
01:02:50,920 --> 01:02:53,280
(I'm afraid your creativity
got frozen that day)

840
01:02:53,360 --> 01:02:55,160
along with your brain.

841
01:02:55,240 --> 01:02:56,320
Are you serious?

842
01:02:56,400 --> 01:02:58,720
(-This is Ko Mi-ran.
-Ko Mi-ran wishes to meet us.)

843
01:02:58,920 --> 01:03:00,240
(I ask for compensation.)

844
01:03:00,320 --> 01:03:01,440
Be quiet!

845
01:03:01,520 --> 01:03:02,600
(Aren't you cold, Dong-chan?)

846
01:03:02,680 --> 01:03:05,800
(You haven't aged at all.
You look exactly the same.)

847
01:03:05,880 --> 01:03:08,040
I was frozen in the freezer, okay?

848
01:03:08,480 --> 01:03:11,400
Director Ma, can you get me a job?

849
01:03:11,640 --> 01:03:12,720
A job?
